==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Internally
<hw>In*ter"nal*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Inwardly; within the enveloping surface, or the boundary of a
thing; within the body; beneath the surface.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Hence: Mentally; spiritually.</def> <rj><au>Jer.
Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Internasal</ent>⟦br⟧
